《'''奧瑪的抉擇'''》({{lang-ar|عمر}}) 是一部2013年[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]剧情片，导演为[[Hany_Abu-Assad|Hany Abu-Assad]]。本片入选[[第66屆坎城影展|第66屆坎城影展]][[一種注目|一種注目]]單元<ref name="Cannes2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/59652.html|title=2013 Official Selection|date=30 April 2013|accessdate=30 April 2013|work=Cannes|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211120304/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/59652.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并赢得评审团大奖<ref name="HWR-UCR">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-missing-picture-wins-regard-558551|title=Cannes: 'The Missing Picture' Wins Un Certain Regard Prize|date=26 May 2013|accessdate=26 May 2013|work=Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528150056/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-missing-picture-wins-regard-558551|dead-url=no}}</ref>。并在同年的[[多伦多电影节|多伦多电影节]]上亮相<ref name="TIFF2013">{{cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/23/toronto-film-festival-lineup |title=Toronto film festival 2013: the full line-up |accessdate=2013-07-24 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2013-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725010702/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jul/23/toronto-film-festival-lineup |dead-url=no }}</ref>。赢得2013年[[亚太影展|亚太影展]]最佳电影<ref>{{cite web|title=Asia Pacific Screen Awards Announced in Australia|work=Australia Network News|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-12-12/an-aspa-winners/5153858|date=13 December 2013|access-date=2014-02-24|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028095946/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-12-12/an-aspa-winners/5153858|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片更获得[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳外语片提名<ref name="Palestine">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/foreign-language-oscar-israel-submits-bethlehem-palestine-goes-with-omar/ |title=Foreign Language Oscar: Israel Submits ‘Bethlehem’; Palestine Goes With ‘Omar’ |accessdate=2013-09-30 |work=Deadline.com |archive-date=2014-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140210113419/http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/foreign-language-oscar-israel-submits-bethlehem-palestine-goes-with-omar/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Oscar Nom">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25757345 |title=Oscars: Main nominations 2014 |accessdate=2014-01-16 |work=BBC News |archive-date=2015-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222154902/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-25757345 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
在巴勒斯坦被占领期间的动荡时代，三位从小玩到大的朋友没有携手并进，反而逐渐走上互相伤害、互相诋毁之路。

