==制作==
导演 Hany Abu-Assad 表示一个晚上他有了拍摄本片的想法，写下故事大纲花费了四个小时，编写剧本耗时仅四天<ref>{{cite web|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/foreign-language-oscar-preview-a-long-list-of-strong-contenders-for-such-a-shortlist-of-possibles/|title=Foreign Language Oscar Preview A Long List Of Strong Contenders For Such a Shortlist Of Possibles Nominees|publisher=Deadline London|date=15 December 2013|access-date=2014-02-24|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709175159/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/foreign-language-oscar-preview-a-long-list-of-strong-contenders-for-such-a-shortlist-of-possibles/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后用了一年时间筹集资金，并于2012年底开拍，取景地包括巴勒斯坦的[[拿撒勒|拿撒勒]]、[[納布盧斯|納布盧斯]]和遥远的[[难民营|难民营]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Ritman|first=Alex|url=http://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/film/hany-abu-assad-presents-a-direct-hit-from-the-west-bank-at-diff|title=Hany Abu-Assad presents a direct hit from the West Bank at DIFF|publisher=[[The_National|The National]]|date=3 December 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140210121653/http://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/film/hany-abu-assad-presents-a-direct-hit-from-the-west-bank-at-diff|archivedate=2014年2月10日|access-date=2014年2月24日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://vimeo.com/79587305|title=AFI FEST: Hany Abu-Assad talks about making of Omar|date=12 November 2013|access-date=2014-02-24|archive-date=2015-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224022954/https://vimeo.com/79587305|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

